AWS Dojo – Data Lake Exercise - https://aws-dojo.com/workshoplists/workshoplist3

AWS Dojo Website for free workshops and exercises - https://aws-dojo.com

AWS Lake Formation is a service that makes it easy to set up a secure data lake in days. A data lake is a centralized, curated, and secured repository that stores all your data, both in its original form and prepared for analysis. This is a demo to see how AWS Data Lake can be accessed by Microsoft Power BI.
